title: Aggregate unique values
sql:
select count ( salary ) salary#,
       count ( distinct salary ) unique_salary#,
       sum ( salary ) salary_total,
       sum ( distinct salary ) unique_salary_total
from   hr.employees e;

SALARY#    UNIQUE_SALARY#    SALARY_TOTAL    UNIQUE_SALARY_TOTAL    
    106                58          684416                 409908
